window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When war comes, the Earth is not ready.</p> <p>An immortals war arrives, the only warning a flash of light and energy 660 million kilometers away. A curiosity, passed off to NASA and tucked away in a note to be ignored. Only the flash of light is not the end, it is the beginning. Admiral Zachary Quinn is about to have a very bad day, and he is not alone.</p> <p>The war is here. Our response must be fast, it must be sure, and it must be victorious.</p> <p>Who wants to live forever?</p>"; 
